      skos:note "Design session notes format. Mixed register: structured markdown with H4 section headers and bold numbered conclusions; embedded Scarlet blockquotes in first person. Antithesis-heavy structure throughout (transform vs. query, actor vs. role, conviction vs. temporality, hard vs. soft). Active voice dominant. Jargon density moderate-high — narr: prefix notation, RDF/SPARQL terms (prov:generated, narr:Actor_*), product terms (compile, TX, layer parameter) used without definition, implying internal audience. Markdown table for architecture summary compresses multi-dimensional information. Average sentence length elevated by quoted speech; prose sections are shorter and punchier." ;
